  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<ul><li>5-day work</li><li>Office hours</li><li>Site office in the East</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare and issue Requests for Quotation (RFQs) for materials and services.</p></li><li><p>Source, review, and evaluate quotations, including price comparisons and cost summaries.</p></li><li><p>Carry out cost planning, cost estimation, and measurement of quantities.</p></li><li><p>Manage project costs, including budget control, variation orders, and main contract claims.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and conclude final account settlements.</p></li><li><p>Administer contracts and oversee contractual compliance.</p></li><li><p>Handle contractual matters such as extensions of time, loss and expense claims, and terms and conditions.</p></li><li><p>Manage subcontractor and supplier progress claims and payment processes.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree in Quantity Surveying or a related discipline.</p></li><li><p>At least 5 years of relevant experience in the construction industry.</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to liaise effectively with clients, subcontractors, and project stakeholders.</p></li><li><p>Good problem-solving abilities and the capacity to work under pressure to meet tight deadlines.<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Kindly email your resume in a detailed Word format to <a href=\"mailto:faith.patman@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>faith.patman@peopleprofilers.com</strong></a></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified</p><p><strong>People Profilers Pte Ltd</strong></p><p>http://www.peopleprofilers.com<br /><br />20 Cecil Street, #08-09 PLUS Building Singapore 049705</p><p>EA License No. 02C4944</p><p>Registration No. R22107092</p><p><br /></p><p></p></li></ul>",
